Installation of the binary windows package (spams_2.3.zip, for i386 and x64)
 a) in the GUI interface of R, select Packages/'Inatsll from zip file'
  and choose spams_2.3.zip
 or b) in R console type :
    install.packages('spams_2.3.zip',repos=NULL)

Note : for a global install under windows-7, you must start R with adminastrator
privileges (right click on the icon)


To run the given examples, open a "command" window and type :
a) on a 32bits system :
cd C:\Program Files\R\R-2.15.1\library\spams\test
..\..\..\bin\Rscript test_spams.R -h
..\..\..\bin\Rscript test_spams.R 

b) on a 64 bits system
..\..\..\bin\x64\Rscript test_spams.R -h
..\..\..\bin\x64\Rscript test_spams.R 
